---
description: Core product behavior and guardrails
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repository builds an Agent Access + Audit Layer for enterprise AI agents.
- The product is not a general chatbot. It is a control plane.
- Every feature should strengthen at least one of these capabilities:
  - identity and ownership
  - permissions and policy enforcement
  - approval for risky actions
  - audit evidence and replay
- Favor boring, inspectable systems over clever magic.
- Prefer implementation choices that make incidents easier to investigate.
- If a requested feature looks flashy but weakens controls, propose a safer version.
